Sentencas: Perovskite oxide samples of (La1-x Pr (x) )(0.6)Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (x = 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8) are obtained by solid-state reaction method.
Titulo: Investigation on Oxygen Chemical Diffusion Properties of Perovskite Oxides (La1-x Pr x )0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The oxygen chemical diffusion properties of (La1-x Pr (x) )(0.6)Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta are determined by electrical conductivity relaxation technique.
Titulo: Investigation on Oxygen Chemical Diffusion Properties of Perovskite Oxides (La1-x Pr x )0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The results show that the conductivity of (La1-x Pr (x) )(0.6)Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta increases with the increase of oxygen partial pressure.
Titulo: Investigation on Oxygen Chemical Diffusion Properties of Perovskite Oxides (La1-x Pr x )0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The (La1-x Pr (x) )(0.6)Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta samples have a high oxygen chemical diffusion coefficient, which decreases linearly with a decrease in temperature and an increase in Pr content.
Titulo: Investigation on Oxygen Chemical Diffusion Properties of Perovskite Oxides (La1-x Pr x )0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The oxygen chemical diffusion coefficient D (chem) remains fairly constant at high PO2.
Titulo: Investigation on Oxygen Chemical Diffusion Properties of Perovskite Oxides (La1-x Pr x )0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The oxygen chemical diffusion coefficient is the highest for (La1-x Pr (x) )(0.6)Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta with x = 0.2, and attains a value of 9.41 x 10(-5) cm(2) s(-1) at 600 A degrees C.
Titulo: Investigation on Oxygen Chemical Diffusion Properties of Perovskite Oxides (La1-x Pr x )0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: This shows the material's promise as a cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Investigation on Oxygen Chemical Diffusion Properties of Perovskite Oxides (La1-x Pr x )0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ
